    <title>日语变形</title>
    <link href="https://janvia.github.io/2018/12/31/%E6%97%A5%E8%AF%AD%E5%8F%98%E5%BD%A2/"/>
    <id>https://janvia.github.io/2018/12/31/日语变形/</id>
    <published>2018-12-31T05:10:40.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-12-31T08:12:17.109Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本篇主要记载日语常用变形，以便个人查询</p><h2 id="动词的敬体"><a href="#动词的敬体" class="headerlink" title="动词的敬体"></a>动词的敬体</h2><h3 id="I类动词"><a href="#I类动词" class="headerlink" title="I类动词"></a>I类动词</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">う段变成い段，再接ます：かく　＝＞　かきます</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="II类动词"><a href="#II类动词" class="headerlink" title="II类动词"></a>II类动词</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">去掉る接ます：みる　＝＞　みます</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="III类动词"><a href="#III类动词" class="headerlink" title="III类动词"></a>III类动词</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">くる　＝＞　きます</span><br><span class="line">する　＝＞　します</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="动词的简体否定型"><a href="#动词的简体否定型" class="headerlink" title="动词的简体否定型"></a>动词的简体否定型</h2><h3 id="I类动词-1"><a href="#I类动词-1" class="headerlink" title="I类动词"></a>I类动词</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">う段变成あ段，再接ない：読む　＝＞　よまない</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="II类动词-1"><a href="#II类动词-1" class="headerlink" title="II类动词"></a>II类动词</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">去掉る接ない：着る　＝＞　きない</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="III类动词-1"><a href="#III类动词-1" class="headerlink" title="III类动词"></a>III类动词</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">くる　＝＞　こない</span><br><span class="line">する　＝＞　しない</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="动词的简体过去式"><a href="#动词的简体过去式" class="headerlink" title="动词的简体过去式"></a>动词的简体过去式</h2><h3 id="I类动词-2"><a href="#I类动词-2" class="headerlink" title="I类动词"></a>I类动词</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">く、ぐ发生“イ音变”：Vく　＝＞　Vいた；　Vぐ　＝＞　Vぃだ</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">う、つ、る发生“促音变”：Vう/つ/る　＝＞　Vった</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ぬ、ぶ、む发生“拨音变”：Vぬ/ぶ/む　＝＞　Vんだ</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">す不发生音变：Vす　＝＞　Vした</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">特殊动词：行く　＝＞　行った</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="II类动词-2"><a href="#II类动词-2" class="headerlink" title="II类动词"></a>II类动词</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">直接去掉“る”,然后接“た”</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="III类动词-2"><a href="#III类动词-2" class="headerlink" title="III类动词"></a>III类动词</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">くる　＝＞　きた</span><br><span class="line">する　＝＞　した</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="动词的能动态"><a href="#动词的能动态" class="headerlink" title="动词的能动态"></a>动词的能动态</h2><p>相当于汉语的“能～，会～，可以～”等意</p><h3 id="I类动词-3"><a href="#I类动词-3" class="headerlink" title="I类动词"></a>I类动词</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">う段变成え段，再接る：送る　＝＞　送れる</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="II类动词-3"><a href="#II类动词-3" class="headerlink" title="II类动词"></a>II类动词</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">去掉る接られる：出る　＝＞　出られる</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="III类动词-3"><a href="#III类动词-3" class="headerlink" title="III类动词"></a>III类动词</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">くる　＝＞　こられる</span><br><span class="line">する　＝＞　できる</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="动词的意志型"><a href="#动词的意志型" class="headerlink" title="动词的意志型"></a>动词的意志型</h2><p>表示意志、建议</p><h3 id="I类动词-4"><a href="#I类动词-4" class="headerlink" title="I类动词"></a>I类动词</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">う段变成お段，再接う：かく　＝＞　かこう</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="II类动词-4"><a href="#II类动词-4" class="headerlink" title="II类动词"></a>II类动词</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">去掉る接ます：あつめる　＝＞　あつめよう</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="III类动词-4"><a href="#III类动词-4" class="headerlink" title="III类动词"></a>III类动词</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">くる　＝＞　こよう</span><br><span class="line">する　＝＞　しよう</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="动词、形容词的条件型"><a href="#动词、形容词的条件型" class="headerlink" title="动词、形容词的条件型"></a>动词、形容词的条件型</h2><p>相当于汉语的“如果～就～、假如～、要是～”等</p><h3 id="I类动词-5"><a href="#I类动词-5" class="headerlink" title="I类动词"></a>I类动词</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">う段变成え段，再接ば：いそぐ　＝＞いそげば</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="II类动词-5"><a href="#II类动词-5" class="headerlink" title="II类动词"></a>II类动词</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">去掉る接れば：おきる　＝＞　おきれば</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="III类动词-5"><a href="#III类动词-5" class="headerlink" title="III类动词"></a>III类动词</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">くる　＝＞　くれば</span><br><span class="line">する　＝＞　しれば</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="形容词"><a href="#形容词" class="headerlink" title="形容词"></a>形容词</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">I类：</span><br><span class="line">去掉i加けれ：たかい　＝＞　たかければ</span><br><span class="line">II类：</span><br><span class="line">接なら，再接ば(现代日语中ば大多省略)：げんき　＝＞　げんきなら(ば)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="动词的ない型"><a href="#动词的ない型" class="headerlink" title="动词的ない型"></a>动词的ない型</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Vない　＝＞　Vなければ</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
